[SHORT DESC]
10% chance to lower Spe 1 stage.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 10% chance to lower the target's Speed one stage.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Bubble is much too weak to be worthy of competitive use. BubbleBeam is undisputably superior, barring PP, and even then, almost everything would prefer to use Surf or Hydro Pump due to their higher Base Power.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/surf">Surf</a> is a more powerful and reliable alternative with no added effect.</p>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/hydro_pump">Hydro Pump</a> is a far more powerful alternative with lower accuracy.</p>